{
  "category": "Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation",
  "description": "Run the admin dashboard health scorer on all 13 hx-* components. Fix any failing dimensions to achieve Grade A (90+) overall score per component.\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Start dev server: `npm run dev:admin` (port 3159)\n2. Check health scores for all 13 components via the admin dashboard\n3. For each component below Grade A: fix the failing dimensions (test coverage, accessibility, token compliance, CEM completeness, story coverage)\n4. Re-run scorer to confirm Grade A\n\n**Key files:**\n- `packages/hx-library/src/components/` — component source\n- `apps/admin/src/lib/health-scorer.ts` — scoring logic\n- `apps/admin/src/app/tests/page.tsx` — test theater\n\n**Acceptance:** All 13 components at Grade A (90+) in admin dashboard.",
  "title": "Run health scorer on all 13 components and fix to Grade A",
