  "descriptionHistory": [
    {
      "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation\n\nRun the admin dashboard health scorer on all 13 components. Fix any dimension scoring below 90 to achieve Grade A (90+) across all 17 dimensions: API docs, CEM completeness, test coverage, accessibility, type safety, docs coverage, story coverage, bundle size, token compliance, Drupal readiness, VRT, cross-browser, code quality, Lit best practices, security, maintainability, DX.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/hx-library/src/components/*/\n- apps/admin/\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] All 13 components score Grade A (90+) on health scorer\n- [ ] No dimension scores below 80\n- [ ] Health score report published to admin dashboard\n- [ ] Remediation documented for any recurring issues\n\n**Complexity:** large",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-27T02:07:33.417Z",
      "source": "initial"
    },
    {
      "description": "Run the admin dashboard health scorer on all 13 hx-* components. Fix any failing dimensions to achieve Grade A (90+) overall score per component.\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Start dev server: `npm run dev:admin` (port 3159)\n2. Check health scores for all 13 components via the admin dashboard\n3. For each component below Grade A: fix the failing dimensions (test coverage, accessibility, token compliance, CEM completeness, story coverage)\n4. Re-run scorer to confirm Grade A\n\n**Key files:**\n- `packages/hx-library/src/components/` — component source\n- `apps/admin/src/lib/health-scorer.ts` — scoring logic\n- `apps/admin/src/app/tests/page.tsx` — test theater\n\n**Acceptance:** All 13 components at Grade A (90+) in admin dashboard.",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-28T06:42:50.974Z",
      "source": "edit"
    }
